# 📖 About the Project

The Student Quiz Application demonstrates the complete **Software Development Life Cycle (SDLC)** by developing a simple quiz management system.

The application allows a student to:

- Register personal information
- Attempt a Python Fundamentals quiz
- Automatically calculate score
- Generate percentage and grade
- Display pass/fail status
- Show an attractive HTML result card
- Present future maintenance features

This project is ideal for beginners learning Python programming.

